org.apache.poi.ss

Enum SpreadsheetVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SpreadsheetVersion>
      • org.apache.poi.ss.SpreadsheetVersion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SpreadsheetVersion> 

    public enum SpreadsheetVersion
extends java.lang.Enum<SpreadsheetVersion>
    This enum allows spreadsheets from multiple Excel versions to be handled by the common code.

    Properties of this enum correspond to attributes of the spreadsheet that are easily discernable to the user. It is not intended to deal with low-level issues like file formats.

    (此枚举允许通用代码处理来自多个Excel版本的电子表格。该枚举的属性对应于用户容易辨别的电子表格的属性。它不打算处理像文件格式这样的低级问题。)

      Excel2007 The total number of available rows is 1M (2^20) The total number of available columns is 16K (2^14) The maximum number of arguments to a function is 255 Number of conditional format conditions on a cell is unlimited (actually limited by available memory in Excel) Number of cell styles is 64000 Length of text cell contents is 32767(Excel 2007可用行总数为1 M（2#20）可用列总数为16 K（2#14）函数的最大参数数为255单元格上的条件格式条件数量是无限的（实际上受Excel中的可用内存限制）单元格样式数量为64000文本单元格内容长度为32767)
      EXCEL97
      Excel97 format aka BIFF8 The total number of available rows is 64k (2^16) The total number of available columns is 256 (2^8) The maximum number of arguments to a function is 30 Number of conditional format conditions on a cell is 3 Number of cell styles is 4000 Length of text cell contents is 32767(Excel97格式又名BIFF 8可用行的总数为64k（2^16）可用列的总数为256（2^8）函数的最大参数数为30单元格上的条件格式条件数为3单元格样式数为4000文本单元格内容长度为32767)
